Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.94,0:00:17.72,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Something's just not right
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.45,0:00:21.99,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在追寻着什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.42,0:00:26.60,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经习惯了谎言 现在也一样 fake your eyes
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.46,0:00:32.74,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The start of century
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.10,0:00:36.24,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切毫无定数
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.27,0:00:41.31,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使一个人也不能哭泣软弱 hate myself
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.61,0:00:51.09,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与真实的痛苦相反的是 埋藏在心中的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.58,0:00:59.90,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在 映射出来 朝着两个人所决定的未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.19,0:01:03.54,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's only my destiny
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.79,0:01:06.91,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝着没有尽头的黑暗前行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.26,0:01:13.25,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里有未知的明天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.54,0:01:18.25,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,oh yeah.You're going nowhere.It's only destiny
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.51,0:01:21.52,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切实的前行着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.81,0:01:28.86,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感受现在 You're in my heart
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.95,0:01:32.90,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're in my heart
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.30,0:22:33.50,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是等待  刺激的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.50,0:22:40.00,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,眼前所见的  全部是重要的所谓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.00,0:22:52.40,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,失去的东西是恐怖的  但我们之间还什么也没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.40,0:22:53.70,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah　yeah  yeah
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.70,0:22:59.80,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,在这蓝蓝的地球上  无限重复未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.80,0:23:04.90,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,can make me free　想要感觉这种跳动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.90,0:23:06.30,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah  yeah  yeah
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.30,0:23:12.30,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,这个心情飞舞升起 染满天空与大海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.30,0:23:22.10,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,紧紧抱住你 想要飞起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.70,0:23:24.90,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah  yeah  yeah
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.90,0:23:31.00,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,这个心情飞舞升起 染满天空与大海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.00,0:23:41.30,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,紧紧抱住你 想要飞起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.60,0:00:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,命运中亦有推理的线索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.30,0:00:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,错综复杂的谜团终有拨云见日的一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.50,0:00:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天是不可思议的绑架事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.30,0:00:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英语的含义令人费解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.90,0:00:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看透真相的是一个外表看似小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.40,0:00:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,智慧却过于常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.50,0:00:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字是 名侦探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.50,0:04:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.50,0:04:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太有意思了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.40,0:04:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,动物们真是可爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.30,0:04:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特别是白狮子的特技
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.90,0:04:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是绝技
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.10,0:04:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为狮子是表演的主角嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.50,0:04:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.70,0:04:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,狮子还被做成了手机链呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.40,0:04:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的 这个吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.00,0:04:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可爱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.70,0:04:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在表演开始之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.20,0:04:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在商店发现的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.30,0:04:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和灰原一起买的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.60,0:04:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也对这种东西感兴趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.50,0:04:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对于那个整天什么都不管 只知道血腥神秘事件的某人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.70,0:04:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可什么也没说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.80,0:04:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要你管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.80,0:04:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是谁 那个被围住的叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.40,0:05:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是这个马戏表演的主办人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.80,0:05:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兰笛·霍克先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.80,0:05:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出生在美国南部俄克拉荷马市的石油大王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.70,0:05:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听说最初收集死去的动物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.90,0:05:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的女儿安妮和斐卢德也在和动物打交道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.80,0:05:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至于现在 是在世界各地举行马戏表演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.70,0:05:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.70,0:05:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看这个册子的最后一页不是有他的照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.30,0:05:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近的兴趣是在表演的同时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.70,0:05:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进行环球旅行并访问了很多国家的动物园
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.00,0:05:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巡回表演的时候如果不带保镖的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.40,0:05:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就会被团团包围
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.60,0:05:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只能自己保护自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.40,0:05:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在电视的特别节目上有发过言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.30,0:05:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日语说得相当流利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.10,0:05:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.90,0:05:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,霍克先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.70,0:05:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使是一句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.20,0:05:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弄错了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.40,0:06:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是霍克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.70,0:06:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你又在开玩笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.10,0:06:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听说你要把表演的一半收入捐给世界各地的动物园
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.40,0:06:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.70,0:06:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.50,0:06:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,3年没有来日本了有什么感想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.90,0:06:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说点什么吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.20,0:06:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,霍克先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.00,0:06:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,霍克先生 霍克先生 拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.40,0:06:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能一下子回答你们所有人的问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.40,0:06:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来自芝加哥的男人(前篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.20,0:06:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被这么多人包围 还真是为难啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.90,0:06:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是潇洒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.30,0:06:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到这里连保镖也不带
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.80,0:06:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被这么多人包围
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.70,0:06:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自作自受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.50,0:06:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别这么说 我们就帮帮他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.80,0:07:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被这么多人重重包围也真够惨的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.10,0:07:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.50,0:07:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以说 我刚刚就已经说过 我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.30,0:07:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 找到了 找到了 汤姆斯先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.10,0:07:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,汤姆斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.90,0:07:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个人不是霍克先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.70,0:07:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是站在那边我们叔叔的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.50,0:07:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是做英语教师的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.60,0:07:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.50,0:07:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.00,0:07:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点走啦 汤姆斯叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.80,0:07:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家不是说好了一起去饭店吃午饭的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.50,0:07:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来啦 快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.20,0:07:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.10,0:07:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了孩子们我才能得救
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.10,0:07:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然经常有人说我和霍克先生很象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.50,0:07:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是象这次一样的误会还是第一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.40,0:07:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道这样 不如变装一下好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.20,0:08:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,变装了更容易让人怀疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.70,0:08:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你真的那么喜欢Paul & Annie的动物表演吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.20,0:08:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢 是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.60,0:08:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们的表演最精彩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.70,0:08:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.30,0:08:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么都想要这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.20,0:08:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以就来日本了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.80,0:08:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那个东西我们也买了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.40,0:08:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是这个手机链在全世界都很畅销的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.60,0:08:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不需要特地跑到日本来买啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.40,0:08:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看看这个手机链的里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.70,0:08:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是写了"Made In Japan"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.80,0:08:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要买到写了这个东西的 就一定要到这里来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.70,0:08:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怪不得 是收藏家收藏的对象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.00,0:08:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.00,0:08:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的意外真是太不幸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.80,0:08:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,表演结束后约好见面的朋友也没见到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.80,0:08:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,见到一个长头发的男子了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.90,0:09:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 因为人太多 所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.20,0:09:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过你倒是很清楚嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.10,0:09:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个人不是霍克先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.30,0:09:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是语言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.90,0:09:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,语... 语言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.70,0:09:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.70,0:09:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚叔叔在说"不能"的意思时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.60,0:09:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把「kant」说成了「ka:nt」 是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.20,0:09:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是昆斯区的英语
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.00,0:09:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在被很多人包围的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.70,0:09:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作为一个地道的南部人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.80,0:09:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说出了英国口音的英语
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.30,0:09:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就觉得有点不对劲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.80,0:09:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么一说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.70,0:09:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在电视上看见的霍克先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.60,0:09:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是个带有南部口音相当豪爽的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.40,0:09:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.00,0:09:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仔细比较相册照片的霍克先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.20,0:09:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脸是不一样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.30,0:09:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是日本记者弄错了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.50,0:09:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不是没有道理的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.40,0:09:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就象外国人很难识别日本人的脸一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.40,0:09:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日本人也只是觉得头发 肤色很象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.80,0:09:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以就弄错了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.60,0:10:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你太厉害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.80,0:10:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字是叫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.30,0:10:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詹姆斯·布兰克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.60,0:10:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.80,0:10:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,江户川柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.50,0:10:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,侦探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.40,0:10:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,江户川
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.60,0:10:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,江户川 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.90,0:10:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,江户川 柯南 侦探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.40,0:10:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,侦探可不是只有柯南一个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.70,0:10:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们都是侦探团的一员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.60,0:10:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.90,0:10:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.20,0:10:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢 夏洛克·福尔摩斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.00,0:10:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你们就是贝克街侦探队咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.00,0:10:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,贝克街
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.10,0:10:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个是帮福尔摩斯收集情报的贝克街小孩们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.60,0:10:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,贝克街是我出生的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.40,0:10:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了 好不容易认识了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.40,0:10:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作为礼物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.40,0:10:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到我非常喜欢的店里请你们吃一顿大餐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.40,0:11:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是开车来的么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.40,0:11:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是这么多人 就没有你的位置了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.10,0:11:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK OK 我开我租的面包车去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.20,0:11:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请等一下 我现在去取
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.80,0:11:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我的驾驶技术不太好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.30,0:11:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就由你来驾驶吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.90,0:11:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,右边方向盘的车太难开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.80,0:11:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔 不习惯右边方向盘的车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.40,0:11:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就说明你现在不住在英国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.20,0:11:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢 是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.90,0:11:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出生在福尔摩斯的伦敦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.10,0:11:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,却是长在芝加哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.40,0:11:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个阿尔·卡彭住过的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.10,0:11:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对那个人有没有什么感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.20,0:11:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.30,0:11:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.40,0:12:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是那样就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.60,0:12:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.60,0:12:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们是警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.40,0:12:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这车是你的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.10,0:12:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 是我租的车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.20,0:12:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.60,0:12:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,实际上这是一辆被盗的车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.10,0:12:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 不会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.20,0:12:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一周前做了被盗遗失登记
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.10,0:12:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请说一下你租车的地点以及当时的情况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.20,0:12:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有你的姓名及居住的酒店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.50,0:12:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站着说不太好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.40,0:12:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到小巷对面的警车上谈吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.70,0:12:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.00,0:13:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会占用你太多时间的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.50,0:13:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.90,0:13:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请上车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.40,0:13:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想起来 我的朋友在等我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.70,0:13:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能不能让我告诉他们我要晚一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.60,0:13:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.60,0:13:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.00,0:13:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老实一点进去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.10,0:13:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.90,0:13:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么东西掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.70,0:13:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是一个手机链
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.00,0:13:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.50,0:13:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.10,0:14:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手指被弄伤了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.10,0:14:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弄伤就弄伤吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.10,0:14:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们不是警察吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.30,0:14:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.30,0:14:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是被包围的爆发户吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.90,0:14:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是 我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.40,0:14:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,热衷于可爱的动物 让你赚了不少钱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.50,0:14:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,分给我们一点吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.00,0:14:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.80,0:14:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经过了40分钟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.50,0:14:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真慢啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.20,0:14:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在干什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.40,0:14:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肚子都瘪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.00,0:14:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那博士在这里等着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.90,0:14:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们大家去看看情况吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.30,0:14:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.70,0:15:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从这里可以走过去的停车场数量并不多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.30,0:15:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,灰原也一起去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.10,0:15:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是这里吧 停车场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.40,0:15:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詹姆斯先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.90,0:15:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 在这里吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.80,0:15:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又不是猫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.80,0:15:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詹姆斯先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.20,0:15:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.00,0:15:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了 一定是这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.30,0:15:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詹姆斯先生的面包车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.90,0:15:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶员的位子前面有一个小狮子玩偶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.70,0:15:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是里面谁也没有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.40,0:15:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,门就这么开着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.10,0:15:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,钥匙也这么插在这
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.60,0:15:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.60,0:15:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在找谁吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.60,0:15:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是要找乘这辆车的长胡子外国人的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.90,0:15:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和两个穿风衣的男人一起去那边了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.70,0:16:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.20,0:16:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.20,0:16:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.10,0:16:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.30,0:16:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.20,0:16:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.60,0:16:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是狮子的手机链
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.90,0:16:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是詹姆斯先生的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.80,0:16:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是这样的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.90,0:16:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是在这里乘了另一辆车走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.10,0:16:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.90,0:16:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詹姆斯先生说过要和朋友见面的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.40,0:16:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道那个外国人把我们给忘记了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.30,0:16:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和别人去什么地方吃饭去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.00,0:16:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.30,0:16:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是忘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.00,0:16:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能詹姆斯先生被卷入什么事件里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.00,0:17:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看 这个手机链
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.70,0:17:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P和&和A被整齐地涂了血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.90,0:17:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许是想对后来找他的我们传达什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.50,0:17:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好了 那
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.80,0:17:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不快点向警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.50,0:17:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,报案的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.20,0:17:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.20,0:17:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.20,0:17:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.40,0:17:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P&A
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.40,0:17:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是容易
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.40,0:17:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下这个爆发户的子女会付多少钱呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.20,0:17:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少也要5亿日元
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.10,0:17:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个家伙对陌生的动物园也会付那么多钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.90,0:17:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该是钱多得不得了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.50,0:18:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是多亏了这部跟真警车一模一样的车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.30,0:18:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有我们勇敢的有名望的霍克先生能被团团包围
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.80,0:18:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连保镖也不带
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.90,0:18:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,错了 我不是霍克先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.60,0:18:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詹姆斯·布兰克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.80,0:18:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们弄错人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.20,0:18:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詹姆斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.80,0:18:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被团团包围后 接下来就是中央情报局了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.50,0:18:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.10,0:18:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是詹姆斯·邦德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.60,0:18:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了 谁都无所谓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.30,0:18:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.90,0:18:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在到我们的老巢之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.50,0:18:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要老实点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.90,0:18:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,007先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.70,0:18:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不如 这样好好领悟一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.00,0:18:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如何拿你的赎身钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.50,0:19:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们可有绝妙的手段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.40,0:19:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我想看的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.20,0:19:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是你们的本事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.90,0:19:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.40,0:19:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从刚才我们就说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.70,0:19:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有个带眼镜的长胡子的外国人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.50,0:19:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被卷入什么事件里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.10,0:19:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有可能是被绑架了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.00,0:19:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你们并没有亲眼看见绑架的画面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.50,0:19:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且带眼镜和有胡子的外国人很多 没办法找啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.30,0:19:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果有照片什么的就另当别论了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.70,0:19:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有啊 要照片的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.10,0:20:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看啊 就是这张脸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.40,0:20:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兰笛·霍克先生啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.10,0:20:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是他的话就没有问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.00,0:20:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才在收音机节目里出现了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.20,0:20:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.60,0:20:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是和兰笛·霍克很象的詹姆斯先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.80,0:20:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个收音机的节目是现场直播的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.40,0:20:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在也在播放中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.20,0:20:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 恐怕是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.60,0:20:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.30,0:20:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果犯人把詹姆斯错当成了霍克而绑架了的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.00,0:20:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就应该会确认霍克先生的播音节目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.80,0:20:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 如果那样的话 不就马上被发现了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.60,0:20:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果发现绑错人以后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.40,0:20:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先 就会没命的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.50,0:20:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 这是怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.40,0:21:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么兰笛·霍克会出现在收音机节目里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.50,0:21:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那 那你是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.60,0:21:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以刚才我说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.20,0:21:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们弄错人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.70,0:21:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该死 怎么会这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.30,0:21:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.40,0:21:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经被这个人看到我们的脸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.70,0:21:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杀掉他就可以了 杀掉他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.50,0:21:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.70,0:21:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想抱着浑身是血的尸体在市区兜风吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.20,0:21:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要把他打到脑浆迸裂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.60,0:21:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然就得按原计划
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.00,0:21:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到群马县的深山里干吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.30,0:21:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个人的问题等一等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.20,0:21:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们重新计划一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.80,0:21:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.20,0:21:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要按计划行事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.20,0:21:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会留下线索的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.70,0:21:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要给警察留下我们的罪证
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.00,0:22:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连绑架这个不知道从哪里来的外国人的理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.40,0:22:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不会知道的
